<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٢٣٣٣ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ:</span> بَلَغَنِي أَنَّ ابْنَ مَسْعُودٍ وَافَقَ عَلِيًّا عَلَى <span class="c2">«أَنَّهَا تَنْتَظِرُهُ أَبَدًا»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>